data.title: University of Pennsylvania Athletics
data.meta_description:
Meg Bender - 2007-08: Senior captain ... Competed in all seven 
events in which Penn participated ... Had a low round of 77 at the Ivy 
League Championships ...
data.text:
2007-08: Senior captain ... Competed in all seven events in which Penn participated ... Had a low round of 77 at the Ivy League Championships ... Penn’s No. 3 in four events ... Shot 77-78-82--237 at Ivy League Championships to finish 19th overall ... Penn’s No. 2 golfer at Princeton invitational, tied for 43rd overall (84-83--167) ... Tied for 29th at Kelly Gutshall Invitational (89-86--175) ... Tied for 50th at Hoya Invitational (87-88-82--257) ... Tied for 45th at ECAC Championships (84-83--167).

2006-07: Did not compete in the fall, as she was travelling abroad ... In the spring, competed in all four tournaments ... Had an 82.4 stroke average in nine rounds ... Low round of 78 two times, at Springlake Invitational and Hoya Invitational ... Penn's No. 3 golfer in three events, tied for second in one ... Shot 80-83-91--254 at Ivy League Championships to finish 24th overall ... Tied for 33rd at Hoya Invite (85-78--163) ... Tied for 43rd at the Springlake Invitational (82-78--160) ... Tied for 48th overall at William & Mary Invitational (80-85--165).

2005-06: Played every round and finished with a team-best 82.1 stroke average ... Low round was an 80, done twice ... Earned All-Ivy honors by tying for sixth with at the Ivy Championships (80 in first round, 42 in nine-hole second round) ... Penn's top finisher at every other event ... Carded 85-82--167 to tie for 37th overall at the Hoya Women's Invitational ... Finished 36th at William & Mary Invitational (83-82--165) ... In the fall, led Quakers at both the Princeton Invitational and the Yale Fall Intercollegiate ... Fired 81-80--161 at Princeton to finish t-25th overall ... Carded 81-84--165 to finish tied for 33rd at Yale.

2004-05: Finished tied for 16th place at the Ivy League Championships after shooting 94-90-82--266 at Maidstone Golf Club ... Penn's top finisher at the Georgetown Invitational, shooting 80 to tie for second place ... Finished 30th at the William & Mary Tribe Invitational with 80-83--163 ... Tied for 20th at the Princeton Fall Invitational after shooting 80-85--165 ... Shot 89-85--174 at the Bucknell Fall Invitational to finish tied for 45th ... Tied for fifth at the Lehigh Fall Invitational, which Penn won, after shooting an 84.
